long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 104106 Fix current session only cookies
This bug is caused by a thinko in COOKIE_RegisterPrefCallbacks, introduced in Blake's Oct 19 nsCookies.cpp v1.86 check-in.
cookie_SetLifetimePref(forCurrentSession ? COOKIE_Normal : COOKIE_Trim);
should obviously be:
cookie_SetLifetimePref(forCurrentSession ? COOKIE_Trim : COOKIE_Normal);

